high_descs: Turn left to reach the passage on the right and head to the bedroom on the left and reach the desk on the right.
Pick up the knife from the desk.
Turn around and take a left turn and reach the kitchen across the passage and reach the lettuce cabinet above the sink.
Cut the lettuce in the cabinet with the knife.
Head to the counter on the left of the sink.
Put the knife on the sink.
Reach the cabinet above the sink.
Pick up the lettuce slice from the cabinet.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to reach the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the lettuce slice on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of lettuce on the sink.

high_descs: Move left, straight, left, straight through doorway, right through another doorway, straight to desk.
To pick up knife from desk.
Turn 90 degrees out of doorway, straight, left, out doorway, straight to sink.
Go to sink with knife.
Turn left with knife away from sink.
To put knife on countertop.
Turn right, back to left by cabinet.
To open cabinet, take lettuce out, close door.
Turn 90 degrees by the fridge.
Open fridge, put lettuce inside, close fridge, open fridge, take lettuce out, close fridge.
To turn left by sink.
To put lettuce on countertop.
anns.task_desc: Get knife from desk, put on countertop, put lettuce on countertop.

high_descs: Turn left and head straight towards the desk, then left into the bedroom, and right into the closet.
Pick up the knife from the desk in the closet.
Exit the closet and the bedroom the way you came in, then go to the kitchen area ahead and to the left.
Cut up the lettuce in the cabinet above the sink.
Look down to the sink.
Place the knife on the panel to the left of the sink.
Look back up to the cabinet with the lettuce.
Remove a piece of lettuce from the plate.
Approach the fridge to your left.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Go back to the sink.
Place the lettuce down next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled piece of Lettuce down next to a Sink.
